  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Add the grated ginger and minced garlic, sauté for another minute.",
    "Add the toor dal, cumin, coriander, and salt. Mix well.",
    "Add the water, bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Add the coconut milk and mix well.",
    "Add the bay leaves and simmer for another 10 minutes.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped cilantro if desired.",
    "Let the pot rest for 5 minutes before serving to allow the flavors to meld."
